!CCCC FOLLOWING SECTION ADDED OCTOBER  2014
!               ***********************************************
!               **  TREAT THE  SET SEARCH  DIRECTORY   CASE  **
!               **             SET SEARCH2 DIRECTORY   CASE  **
!               **             SET SEARCH3 DIRECTORY   CASE  **
!               **             SET SEARCH4 DIRECTORY   CASE  **
