!                                         (SET QMS/QUIC PORTRAIT MARGINS)
!                                         (SET QMS/QUIC PPI)
!     UPDATED         --AUGUST     1988   (SET POSTSCRIPT FONT)
!                                         (SET POSTSCRIPT LANDSCAPE MARGINS)
